creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Short Story Collection Vol. 063 by Various.
Read in English by Peter Yearsley; John Burlinson; Craig Campbell; VfkaBT; Phil Schempf; David Wales; Tony Addison; Son of the Exiles; Newgatenovelist; Michele Fry; Pierce Waltz
This collection comprises 20 short stories of various genres, chosen by the readers.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
